@startuml
title ArcHub CMS - Webhook Application Service
skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam defaultFontName Arial

actor "Editor / admin UI" as Editor
component "Webhook admin routes" as Routes
component "ArcHubMaintenanceService" as Maintenance
component "ArcHubWebhookService\napplication.webhooks" as Webhooks
component "ArcHubDomainEvent" as Event
component "ArcHubCMSService\ncompatibility API" as CMS
database "SQLite CMS store" as DB
cloud "External webhook receiver" as Receiver

Editor --> Routes : manage subscriptions\ninspect deliveries\ndispatch manually
Routes --> Webhooks : subscriptions / upsert\ndeliveries / dispatch_pending
Maintenance --> Webhooks : scheduled dispatch_pending
Webhooks --> CMS : list/upsert/dispatch methods
CMS --> DB : subscriptions\ndelivery queue\nattempt log
CMS --> Receiver : signed HTTP request
Webhooks --> Event : subscription.upserted\ndispatch.completed
Webhooks --> Routes : compatible JSON payload
@enduml
